main event: Two unidentified objects were observed entering the atmosphere, one shaped like an oval and the other resembling a 5-inch pencil.
interesting points: The first object was seen closely, while the second object was viewed from a distance., The first object appeared white and turned orange just before disappearing., Duration of the sighting was about 5 seconds., The objects were reported to have no tails., A military aircraft was involved in the observation.
sighted object: an oval object and a pencil-shaped object
witness description: 1st Lt. 965th AEW&C Squadron, aircraft commander, 4,099 flying hours
